profile:
Universal PAINTING WAS ESTABLISHED IN 1985 by its owner and operator Andy Cliff.

Our goal then as it is now is to bring a higher quality product to the Peterborough area than is typically available.This mindset has served us well since our inception as we have maintained this standard for 34 years.
We offer high quality painting services including a through approach to surface repairs to both drywall and plaster, wallpaper stripping as well as exterior decoration , pressure washing caulking genie man lift services and expert consultation.

We offer our skills to new build homeowners and general contractors; to landlords,. we work with The city and county of Peterborough, shop owners, institutions and our favorite, the mom and pop homeowners
who without we could not reach our goals of personal service and that of community recognition as the go to guys for all your decorative dreams.

Myself and my team work hard each day to fulfill our clients dreams of a perfect painting project and to earn the thank yous and hand shakes at the end your project.
This commitment of guaranteed satisfaction,of a better standard of workmanship, of integrity in all things has brought to us the gratitude of thousands of satisfied customers.

At Universal Painting, customer satisfaction is at the heart of our business. That’s why we don’t leave a job site unless the paint job is fit for your approval. We complete both interior and exterior painting jobs in Peterborough for residential, commercial and industrial properties. No matter the size of the project, we work to stay within your timeline and budget.

***

Our contract painting services include:

Exterior painting
 
Interior painting and finishing
 
Apartment repaints
 
Deck sanding and staining
 
Drywall and plaster repairs
 
Sealing of smoke damaged living spaces
 
Floor coatings
 
Painting of sea containers
 
Painting of infrastructure and housing initiatives

***

Call Andy at Universal Painting and talk painting!

Call or Text 705 927 0060 or Email at brushwithsuccess@gmail.com
services:
Spray,brush and roller applications
Drywall and Plaster repairs
Caulking
High Pressure washing
